{"tid":2382713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以色列施打輝瑞疫苗傳捷報 保護率達99.985％","createTime":"2021-01-27T12:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T15:33:53.000Z","uid":280261,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"46b015258a21dc1ae5b74e607bbb7bff8bfc1995","tid":2382713,"uid":280261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕以色列為民眾施打輝瑞武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫苗後傳出好消息，保護率超過輝瑞之前公布的95％，達到99.985％的驚人數字。<br />\n<br />\n據《以色列時報》 報導，以色列馬卡比健保系統（Maccabi Healthcare Services）指出，12萬8000人接種了武肺疫苗第2劑，1週之後只有20人染疫，比率低到0.015％。<br />\n<br />\n免疫學家科恩（Cyrille Cohen）透露，在該週內以色列總人口約有0.65％確診，因此雖然馬卡比的資料缺乏對照樣本，但如果將整個以色列視為不完美的對照組，的確高於輝瑞臨床試驗的95％有效性。<br />\n<br />\n科恩說，這令人興奮的結果證實了輝瑞疫苗的高保護率。馬卡比分析師佐哈爾（Anat Ekka Zohar）也表示，儘管這是非常早期的數據，但也是相當重要的資料，因為全世界都在透過以色列了解疫苗功效如何。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom 自由時報"},{"pid":"6aeeb5c8b7583157c2c96494bce738b10cfa2ae9","tid":2382713,"uid":280261,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:40:05.000Z","msg":"外國造假，愛國一定要打國產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72f9dafb501a8222e854666745e3b216be89dd1","tid":2382713,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:52:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3422878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3422878&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn0UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=6b830926\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3422878&h=face6f78\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3422878</a>"},{"pid":"49871cb592900704b803be633abfbd542fa8bda5","tid":2382713,"uid":155895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"思煙bb打左就唔洗死"},{"pid":"b9f42d8ad2f219aa5ead097cd48720bdec67b8db","tid":2382713,"ui